# ExternalPurchaseCustomLink.NoticeResult.cancelled

**Case**

The customer chooses to cancel; don’t offer external purchases.

## Declaration

```swift
case cancelled
```

## Getting notice results

- **ExternalPurchaseCustomLink.NoticeResult.continued**: The customer chooses to continue; the app can offer external purchases.
